summary: An ordinance authorizing and directing the levy and collection of a supplemental assessment or re-assessment to pay the deficiency in the cost and expense of the improvement of 23rd Avenue West and 23rd Avenue West produced, from the intersection of West Garfield Street to West Newton Street, by constructing a bridge roadway thereon 26 feet in width, and by doing such grading as may be necessary, under Ordinance No. 26851, creating Local Improvement District No. 2482, of the City of Seattle, and providing for the payment therefor.
